name: .FZIP File Extension
summary: Learn about .FZIP files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Add-on for Foxit Reader, a small and fast PDF viewing program; adds extra features to the program, such as language support, JavaScript support, image decoding, and content management features.

content: FZIP files can be installed by selecting the "Install Updates" feature located in the Foxit Reader Help menu. The add-on will be installed in the Foxit Reader install directory.
